🔐 Security Layer (Financial Grade)
	•	IAM Roles for Service Accounts (IRSA)
	•	AWS Secrets Manager (NO Kubernetes secrets for sensitive data)
	•	KMS encryption (EBS, S3, secrets)
	•	Private cluster endpoints (optional for high security)
	•	VPC isolation per environment (prod/stage/dev)

⸻

📊 Observability Layer
	•	CloudWatch Logs (centralized)
	•	CloudWatch Metrics (baseline)
	•	Prometheus (selective use only)
	•	Grafana dashboards (team-level visibility)
	•	S3 archival for logs (cost control)

